{"tid":2251408,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權到浩園獻花　悼念72位殉職同僚","createTime":"2020-10-20T19:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T00:59:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f59129cdd7c9cbf3f0ebba332b1dedc40a101e","tid":2251408,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"本周日（25日）就是重陽節，公務員事務局局長聶德權今日（20日）到浩園，向72位因公殉職的同事獻花，代表同僚表達哀悼及敬意。<br />\n<br />\n十年前馬尼拉人質事件中過身的港人，被下葬在浩園旁的景仰園。聶德權今在其社交平台表示，當年人質事件發生後，社會福利署聯同多個政府部門，為死傷者家屬提供支援，當時他是社署署長，而今日則以另一身份向事件中去世港人表達哀思。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2781975/%E8%81%B6%E5%BE%B7%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%B0%E6%B5%A9%E5%9C%92%E7%8D%BB%E8%8A%B1%E3%80%80%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B572%E4%BD%8D%E6%AE%89%E8%81%B7%E5%90%8C%E5%83%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2781975%2F%25E8%2581%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%258D%25BB%25E8%258A%25B1%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%25BF%25B572%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%25AE%2589%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2583%259A&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QSLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=c817e71a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2781975/%E8%81%B6%E5%BE%B7%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%B0%E6%B5%A9%E5%9C%92%E7%8D%BB%E8%8A%B1%E3%80%80%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B572%E4%BD%8D%E6%AE%89%E8%81%B7%E5%90%8C%E5%83%9A</a>"},{"pid":"2fa33a5fff4fd3ad43934abdd15e90a252ae4265","tid":2251408,"uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"真係笑撚咗<br />\n馬尼拉人質事件中被遺容嘅女人最後要到台灣做重建手術<br />\n垃圾共狗又想出嚟抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31599c9b0adf27b1f4970e238e1153ba18cd9bd9","tid":2251408,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa33a5fff4fd3ad43934abdd15e90a252ae4265","tid":2251408,"uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"真係笑撚咗<br />\n馬尼拉人質事件中被遺容嘅女人最後要到台